metadata.name: WT Pride NFT
metadata.description:
To celebrate Pride Month, we have created our official Women Tribe Pride NFT!

- 75% of primary sales will proceed to OutRight Action International!

- The remaining 25% of primary sales and 100% of secondary sales will go to our DAO fund!

The price of each NFT is set at 0.02 ETH and there are a total of 2022 editions.
